            <column name="category" value="Returns"/>
            <column name="title" value="How to return a product"/>
            <column name="slug" value="how-to-return-product"/>
            <column name="body" value="To return a product on HomeBase: 1. Go to My Account > My Orders. 2. Select the order and click 'Return'. 3. Choose a reason for return and upload photos if the item is damaged. 4. Select pickup or self-ship as the return method. 5. Pack the item in its original packaging. For pickup returns, a courier will collect the item within 2-3 business days. Refunds are processed within 5 business days after we receive the item. Return window: 7 days for most items, 10 days for electronics. Non-returnable items: innerwear, perishables, personal care, customized products, gift cards."/>
            <column name="author" value="support-team"/>
